  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Box #341 is trying to return to its spot in the warehouse—by cleverly flipping itself and using liquids with unique abilities!<br><br><strong>Flip, Dip, and reach the Goal !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of strategy and creativity in this delightful puzzle adventure! The challenges revolve around harnessing the unique potential of the Box's sides—dip into various liquids to grant each face special properties. Align these enhanced sides with the right slopes to trigger flips and navigate your way through clever, handcrafted levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/81ec958b7f0090ddf8ff24c6e6b20734.poster.avif?t=1758668438\" width=722 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/81ec958b7f0090ddf8ff24c6e6b20734.webm?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/81ec958b7f0090ddf8ff24c6e6b20734.mp4?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combination of Elements!</strong><br><br>Immerse yourself in intricately designed levels that encourage creative exploration and experimentation! Each challenge invites you to discover the possibilities of combining various game elements. As you develop your skills and master strategic gameplay, the game raises the fun with increasingly complex levels that test your abilities to the fullest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/72edd487eceb37c2af0c119dfd2db737.poster.avif?t=1758668438\" width=650 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/72edd487eceb37c2af0c119dfd2db737.webm?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/72edd487eceb37c2af0c119dfd2db737.mp4?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Cozy Experience</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a heartwarming and cozy experience centered around an endearing box on a simple quest for happiness—flipping to the right face! Along the way, meet charming NPCs who bring humor and cuteness to life in the warehouse. Immerse yourself in a delightful experience and discover the mystery outside the warehouse!<strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/5828e5b21e6fbe19e917a13fcc9f063a.poster.avif?t=1758668438\" width=650 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/5828e5b21e6fbe19e917a13fcc9f063a.webm?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/5828e5b21e6fbe19e917a13fcc9f063a.mp4?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Box #341 is trying to return to its spot in the warehouse—by cleverly flipping itself and using liquids with unique abilities!<br><br><strong>Flip, Dip, and reach the Goal !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of strategy and creativity in this delightful puzzle adventure! The challenges revolve around harnessing the unique potential of the Box's sides—dip into various liquids to grant each face special properties. Align these enhanced sides with the right slopes to trigger flips and navigate your way through clever, handcrafted levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/81ec958b7f0090ddf8ff24c6e6b20734.poster.avif?t=1758668438\" width=722 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/81ec958b7f0090ddf8ff24c6e6b20734.webm?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/81ec958b7f0090ddf8ff24c6e6b20734.mp4?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combination of Elements!</strong><br><br>Immerse yourself in intricately designed levels that encourage creative exploration and experimentation! Each challenge invites you to discover the possibilities of combining various game elements. As you develop your skills and master strategic gameplay, the game raises the fun with increasingly complex levels that test your abilities to the fullest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/72edd487eceb37c2af0c119dfd2db737.poster.avif?t=1758668438\" width=650 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/72edd487eceb37c2af0c119dfd2db737.webm?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/72edd487eceb37c2af0c119dfd2db737.mp4?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Cozy Experience</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a heartwarming and cozy experience centered around an endearing box on a simple quest for happiness—flipping to the right face! Along the way, meet charming NPCs who bring humor and cuteness to life in the warehouse. Immerse yourself in a delightful experience and discover the mystery outside the warehouse!<strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/5828e5b21e6fbe19e917a13fcc9f063a.poster.avif?t=1758668438\" width=650 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/5828e5b21e6fbe19e917a13fcc9f063a.webm?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445150/extras/5828e5b21e6fbe19e917a13fcc9f063a.mp4?t=1758668438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
